---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer>
  <img src="/assets/logo-black.png" alt="Lovable" />
  <span>© {year} Българска Lovable Общност · communitylovable.bg</span>
  <span class="spacer"></span>
  <span>Неофициална общност, водена от доброволци</span>
</footer>

<style>
  footer {
    max-width: 1240px;
    margin: 40px auto 0;
    padding: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--faint);
    font-weight: 600;
    align-items: center;
  }
  footer img { height: 16px; object-fit: contain; opacity: 0.5; }
  .spacer { flex: 1; }
</style>
